  "detailed_description": "The invaders are trying to runsack the earth, can you stop them and avoid getting shot in the process?<br><br>You control a ship and your main objective is to shoot down the enemy ships one by one till none stands.<br><br>As you make your way through the levels the difficulty level also ramps up be ready to face new enemy types, traps and even control two ships at the same time.<br><br>Also.... you only have one life, are you up to the challenge?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274990/extras/1736379497edd57381df87a808101fee.poster.avif?t=1675073693\" width=674 height=506 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274990/extras/1736379497edd57381df87a808101fee.webm?t=1675073693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274990/extras/1736379497edd57381df87a808101fee.mp4?t=1675073693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Over 30 challenging levels to blaze through at launch<br></li><li> Enemy types that can adapt their speed, firing rate and more<br></li><li> Traps to avoid like asteroid belts and times bombs<br></li><li> A puzzly feeling in some levels</li></ul>",
